  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lew</b> is a common male name and nickname in Westeros. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lew_(guard)\" title=\"Lew (guard)\">Lew</a>, a guard at Winterfell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Left_Hand_Lew\" title=\"Left Hand Lew\">Left Hand Lew</a>, a steward of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewys_Piper\" title=\"Lewys Piper\">Little Lew Piper</a>, the nickname of Lewys Piper, a squire to Jaime Lannister</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Long_Lew\" title=\"Long Lew\">Long Lew</a>, a guard at Riverrun</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lew&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewyn_Martell\" title=\"Lewyn Martell\">Lewyn Martell</a>, a member of the Kingsguard during the reign of Aerys II Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewys\" title=\"Lewys\">Lewys</a> (disambiguation)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404214200\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14718-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404214200 and revision id 323460\n -->\n",
